headline: Deere (DE): Valuation Check After Trump Targets Farm Equipment Costs and Farmer Aid Package
summary: Deere (DE) just found itself in Washingtons spotlight after President Trump blasted the high cost of farm equipment and paired that critique with a $12 billion aid package aimed at struggling farmers. See our latest analysis for Deere. That political pressure helps explain why Deere’s 1 day share price return of 1.5% to $475.94 comes after a choppy spell, even as its year to date share price return of 13.8% and five year total shareholder return of 91.9% point to still solid, if slower,...

headline: As Trump Takes a Stand Against Deere, How Should You Play the Blue-Chip Dividend Stock?
summary: As Donald Trump asked Deere to lower agricultural equipment prices, let us look at which ETFs are affected by the manufacturing giant.
